                            Overview of the GSK Exit Exam Questions and Answers
                        </h2>
                        
                        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            The General Ship Knowledge (GSK) exit exam is a core assessment for candidates pursuing their GP Rating certification. Demonstrating a solid grasp of basic deck seamanship, safety equipment, and vessel layout is essential to pass this modular assessment. To prepare seafarers thoroughly, this page offers a dedicated <strong>gsk online test</strong> platform consisting of authentic, updated <strong>gsk question</strong> sets.
                        </p>

