                        </h3>
                        
                        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            While using our online practice interface is highly recommended, seafarers frequently experience spotty internet connections at sea or during travel. To make sure your prep never halts, we offer a dedicated <strong>Gsk exit exam practice pdf free download</strong>.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            By utilizing this offline PDF, you can:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 mb-6">
                            <li>Access offline prep materials containing essential <strong>GP Exit Exam practice questions</strong> anytime.</li>
