                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                                        </svg>
                                    </span>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-body leading-relaxed border-t border-hairline pt-4">
                                    Bright Mariner provides the best interactive <strong>gsk online test</strong> room on this page. Our platform lets you practice authentic <strong>gsk question</strong> sets that are regularly updated to match the latest DG Shipping online databases.
                                </div>
                            </details>

                            <details class="group bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
